1. Imam *brus* za oštrice. (I have a *sharpener* for blades.)
2. Nije mi jasno zašto ne nosi *brus*. (I don't understand why she doesn't wear a *bra*.)
3. Vidim da si obukla novi *brus* koji ti savršeno stoji. (I see you're wearing a new *bra* that fits you perfectly.)
4. Moram da kupim novi *brus* jer su mi stari postali premali. (I need to buy a new *bra* because my old ones have become too small.)
5. *Brus* je bio jedan od najvažnijih gradova u srednjem veku. (The city of *Brus* was one of the most important cities in the Middle Ages.)
6. Zaboravio sam da stavim *brus* u torbu za trening. (I forgot to put my *athletic supporter* in my gym bag.)
7. Treba mi *brus* za brušenje kamenja. (I need a *grinder* for polishing stones.)
8. Naša kompanija proizvodi različite vrste *brusnih ploča*. (Our company produces various types of *grinding discs*.)
9. Moram da obučem *brus* za skijanje pre nego što krenemo na stazu. (I need to put on my *ski goggles* before we hit the slopes.)
10. Čišćenje kamenog zida može biti teško bez odgovarajućeg *brusa*. (Cleaning a stone wall can be difficult without the proper *brush*.)